                      <span>2001-10-12</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>Which stands for "Compact, Complete, and Comprehensible".<br>It is fairly easy to read, has every basic aspects of Category Theory, and has a lot of good examples.<br>If you would like to know the first step of Category Theory and you are in CS realm, this book is the one you have to try.</span>
                  
              
